title: Dock
description: An implementation of the MacOS dock using react + tailwindcss + framer motion
author: dillionverma

body.raw:
<ComponentPreview name="dock-demo" />

## Installation

<Tabs defaultValue="cli">

<TabsList>
  <TabsTrigger value="cli">CLI</TabsTrigger>
  <TabsTrigger value="manual">Manual</TabsTrigger>
</TabsList>
<TabsContent value="cli">

```bash
npx magicui-cli add dock
```

</TabsContent>

<TabsContent value="manual">

<Steps>

<Step>Copy and paste the following code into your project.</Step>

<ComponentSource name="dock" />

<Step>Update the import paths to match your project setup.</Step>

</Steps>

</TabsContent>

</Tabs>

## Examples

### Custom Direction

<ComponentPreview name="dock-demo-2" />

### Custom magnification

<ComponentPreview name="dock-demo-3" />

## Props

### Dock

| Prop          | Type      | Description                          | Default  |
| ------------- | --------- | ------------------------------------ | -------- |
| className     | string    | Custom CSS class for styling         | -        |
| children      | ReactNode | Children elements                    | -        |
| magnification | number    | Level of icon magnification          | 60       |
| distance      | number    | Distance from cursor to magnify icon | 140      |
| direction     | string    | Direction of the dock                | "bottom" |

### DockIcon

| Prop          | Type              | Description                          | Default |
| ------------- | ----------------- | ------------------------------------ | ------- |
| size          | number            | Size of the icon                     | -       |
| magnification | number            | Level of icon magnification          | 60      |
| distance      | number            | Distance from cursor to magnify icon | 140     |
| mouseX        | any               | Mouse X position for magnification   | -       |
| className     | string            | Custom CSS class for styling         | -       |
| children      | React.ReactNode   | Children elements                    | -       |
| props         | PropsWithChildren | Additional props                     | -       |

## Credits

- Credits to [Build UI](https://buildui.com/recipes/magnified-dock) for this fantastic component
- Credits to [Ritesh Bucha](https://twitter.com/bucha_ritesh) for finding and improving it

const DATA = {\r
  navbar: [\r
    { href: "#", icon: HomeIcon, label: "Home" },\r
    { href: "#", icon: PencilIcon, label: "Blog" },\r
  ],\r
  contact: {\r
    social: {\r
      GitHub: {\r
        name: "GitHub",\r
        url: "#",\r
        icon: Icons.github,\r
      },\r
      LinkedIn: {\r
        name: "LinkedIn",\r
        url: "#",\r
        icon: Icons.linkedin,\r
      },\r
      X: {\r
        name: "X",\r
        url: "#",\r
        icon: Icons.x,\r
      },\r
      email: {\r
        name: "Send Email",\r
        url: "#",\r
        icon: Icons.email,\r
      },\r
    },\r
  },\r
};\r
\r
export function DockDemo() {\r
  return (\r
    <div className="relative flex h-[500px] w-full flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg border bg-background md:shadow-xl">\r
      <span className="pointer-events-none whitespace-pre-wrap bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-gray-300/80 bg-clip-text text-center text-8xl font-semibold leading-none text-transparent dark:from-white dark:to-slate-900/10">\r
        Dock\r
      </span>\r
      <TooltipProvider>\r
        <Dock direction="middle">\r
          {DATA.navbar.map((item) => (\r
            <DockIcon key={item.label}>\r
              <Tooltip>\r
                <TooltipTrigger asChild>\r
                  <Link\r
                    href={item.href}\r
                    className={cn(\r
                      buttonVariants({ variant: "ghost", size: "icon" }),\r
                      "size-12 rounded-full",\r
                    )}\r
                  >\r
                    <item.icon className="size-4" />\r
                  </Link>\r
                </TooltipTrigger>\r
                <TooltipContent>\r
                  <p>{item.label}</p>\r
                </TooltipContent>\r
              </Tooltip>\r
            </DockIcon>\r
          ))}\r
          <Separator orientation="vertical" className="h-full" />\r
          {Object.entries(DATA.contact.social).map(([name, social]) => (\r
            <DockIcon key={name}>\r
              <Tooltip>\r
                <TooltipTrigger asChild>\r
                  <Link\r
                    href={social.url}\r
                    className={cn(\r
                      buttonVariants({ variant: "ghost", size: "icon" }),\r
                      "size-12 rounded-full",\r
                    )}\r
                  >\r
                    <social.icon className="size-4" />\r
                  </Link>\r
                </TooltipTrigger>\r
                <TooltipContent>\r
                  <p>{name}</p>\r
                </TooltipContent>\r
              </Tooltip>\r
            </DockIcon>\r
          ))}\r
          <Separator orientation="vertical" className="h-full py-2" />\r
          <DockIcon>\r
            <Tooltip>\r
              <TooltipTrigger asChild>\r
                <ModeToggle className="rounded-full" />\r
              </TooltipTrigger>\r
              <TooltipContent>\r
                <p>Theme</p>\r
              </TooltipContent>\r
            </Tooltip>\r
          </DockIcon>\r
        </Dock>\r
      </TooltipProvider>\r
    </div>\r
  );\r
}\r

client";\r
\r
import React, { PropsWithChildren, useRef } from "react";\r
import { cva, type VariantProps } from "class-variance-authority";\r
import { motion, useMotionValue, useSpring, useTransform } from "framer-motion";\r
\r
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";\r
\r
export interface DockProps extends VariantProps<typeof dockVariants> {\r
  className?: string;\r
  magnification?: number;\r
  distance?: number;\r
  direction?: "top" | "middle" | "bottom";\r
  children: React.ReactNode;\r
}\r
\r
const DEFAULT_MAGNIFICATION = 60;\r
const DEFAULT_DISTANCE = 140;\r
\r
const dockVariants = cva(\r
  "mx-auto w-max mt-8 h-[58px] p-2 flex gap-2 rounded-2xl border supports-backdrop-blur:bg-white/10 supports-backdrop-blur:dark:bg-black/10 backdrop-blur-md",\r
);\r
\r
const Dock = React.forwardRef<HTMLDivElement, DockProps>(\r
  (\r
    {\r
      className,\r
      children,\r
      magnification = DEFAULT_MAGNIFICATION,\r
      distance = DEFAULT_DISTANCE,\r
      direction = "bottom",\r
      ...props\r
    },\r
    ref,\r
  ) => {\r
    const mouseX = useMotionValue(Infinity);\r
\r
    const renderChildren = () => {\r
      return React.Children.map(children, (child: any) => {\r
        return React.cloneElement(child, {\r
          mouseX: mouseX,\r
          magnification: magnification,\r
          distance: distance,\r
        });\r
      });\r
    };\r
\r
    return (\r
      <motion.div\r
        ref={ref}\r
        onMouseMove={(e) => mouseX.set(e.pageX)}\r
        onMouseLeave={() => mouseX.set(Infinity)}\r
        {...props}\r
        className={cn(dockVariants({ className }), {\r
          "items-start": direction === "top",\r
          "items-center": direction === "middle",\r
          "items-end": direction === "bottom",\r
        })}\r
      >\r
        {renderChildren()}\r
      </motion.div>\r
    );\r
  },\r
);\r
\r
Dock.displayName = "Dock";\r
\r
export interface DockIconProps {\r
  size?: number;\r
  magnification?: number;\r
  distance?: number;\r
  mouseX?: any;\r
  className?: string;\r
  children?: React.ReactNode;\r
  props?: PropsWithChildren;\r
}\r
\r
const DockIcon = ({\r
  size,\r
  magnification = DEFAULT_MAGNIFICATION,\r
  distance = DEFAULT_DISTANCE,\r
  mouseX,\r
  className,\r
  children,\r
  ...props\r
}: DockIconProps) => {\r
  const ref = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);\r
\r
  const distanceCalc = useTransform(mouseX, (val: number) => {\r
    const bounds = ref.current?.getBoundingClientRect() ?? { x: 0, width: 0 };\r
\r
    return val - bounds.x - bounds.width / 2;\r
  });\r
\r
  let widthSync = useTransform(\r
    distanceCalc,\r
    [-distance, 0, distance],\r
    [40, magnification, 40],\r
  );\r
\r
  let width = useSpring(widthSync, {\r
    mass: 0.1,\r
    stiffness: 150,\r
    damping: 12,\r
  });\r
\r
  return (\r
    <motion.div\r
      ref={ref}\r
      style={{ width }}\r
      className={cn(\r
        "flex aspect-square cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-full",\r
        className,\r
      )}\r
      {...props}\r
    >\r
      {children}\r
    </motion.div>\r
  );\r
};\r
\r
DockIcon.displayName = "DockIcon";\r
\r
export { Dock, DockIcon, dockVariants };\r
